cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SI 

The paper deals with learning from data, which is a core topic in machine learning (cs.LG). It also heavily relies on information theory (cs.IT) and Bayesian methods (cs.AI). The use of PAC-Bayes bounds and ensemble learning methods suggests a focus on statistical learning theory (cs.ST) and data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper introduces new hypotheses about the generalization of parameters, which could fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
